dc_description_s: Shows railroads and county boundaries. Relief shown by hachures. Inset: Northern part of New York. In upper right corner: "39." From Bradley's atlas of the world for commercial and library reference. 1 map: col.; 39 x 54 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
